sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as Client / load generator
  participant Web as web-app
  participant Mon as monitoring-service
  participant HEC as Splunk HEC

  Client->>Web: HTTP request
  Web->>Web: handle endpoint + timing middleware
  Web-->>Client: response
  Web->>Mon: async POST /ingest (fire-and-forget)
  Mon->>HEC: Authorization: Splunk token
  Note over Mon,HEC: Failures swallowed so apps stay up if Splunk is down
